<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>EC-16 CONTROLLER - TROUBLESHOOTING - TESTING THE MODULATOR, PART A</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc id="hl0403219" svcproctype="troubleshoot" graphiccount="1">
        <title>TESTING THE MODULATOR, PART A</title>
        <para>Refer to
            <hotlnk xrefid="f0403210">Figure 10</hotlnk>.
        </para>
        <figure id="f0403210" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g0403210" filename="../figg04/G0403210.webp" type="webp"/>
            <caption>Figure 10. Testing the Modulator, Part A</caption>
        </figure>
        <table id="hl0403222">
            <title>Testing the Modulator, Part A</title>
            <tgroup cols="5">
                <colspec colname="1" colwidth="0.83in"/>
                <colspec colname="2" colwidth="0.79in"/>
                <colspec colname="3" colwidth="1.80in"/>
                <colspec colname="4" colwidth="1.35in"/>
                <colspec colname="5" colwidth="1.65in"/>
                <spanspec namest="1" nameend="5" spanname="s1t5"/>
                <thead>
                    <row rowsep="0">
                        <entry colname="1" align="center">
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">STEP</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2" align="center">
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">KEY</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="3" align="center">
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">ACTION</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="4" align="center">
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">YES-IN SPEC.</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="5" align="center">
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">NO-OUT OF SPEC.</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <row rowsep="0">
                        <entry colname="1">
                            <para>1.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2">
                            <para>Off</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="3">
                            <para>Turn ignition OFF and disconnect wire harness connector from EC-16. Probe connector
                                with volt/ohm meter and note that proper resistance values are obtained for modulator
                                being tested (
                                <hotlnk xrefid="hl0403225">Resistance Values Table</hotlnk>). Are resistance values
                                correct?
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="4">
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="5">
                            <para>Go to
                                <hotlnk document="s04032_HL0403224.xml" xrefid="hl0403224">TESTING THE MODULATOR, PART
                                    B</hotlnk>.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row rowsep="0">
                        <entry colname="1">
                            <para>2.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2">
                            <para>Off/On</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="3">
                            <para>Inspect connector and reconnect to EC-16. Turn ignition ON and pass magnet over RESET
                                on EC-16. Note reaction of red LEDs. Are any red LEDs illuminated?
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="4">
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="5">
                            <para>Repeat
                                <hotlnk document="s04032_HL0403208.xml" xrefid="hl0403208">INITIAL START-UP
                                    PROCEDURE</hotlnk>. If this test step has repeated twice,
                                <emph type="bold">replace the EC-16.</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row rowsep="0">
                        <entry colname="1">
                            <para>3.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2">
                            <para>On</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="3">
                            <para>Same red LEDs illuminated?</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="4">
                            <para>Replace the EC-16.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="5">
                            <para>Go to
                                <hotlnk document="s04032_HL0403214.xml" xrefid="hl0403214">INSPECTION FOR ILLUMINATED
                                    LEDS, PART III</hotlnk>, and retest.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                </tbody>
            </tgroup>
        </table>
        <table id="hl0403225">
